import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-instructor-dashboard', templateUrl: './dashboard.component.html', styleUrls: ['./dashboard.component.css'] }) export class InstructorDashboardComponent { constructor(private router: Router) {} goTo(page: string) { switch (page) { case 'create': this.router.navigate(['/instructor/create-batch']); break; case 'create-course': this.router.navigate(['/instructor/create-course']); break; case 'view-bookings': this.router.navigate(['/instructor/view-bookings']); break; } } }

Instructor Dashboard

Manage your hairstyling batches, bookings, and view your student enrollments.

Create New Batch

Add a new training batch for students.

Create New Course

Add a new training course for students.
